The paper presents a proof method recommendation system for Isabelle/HOL, which is a theorem proving system used in formal verification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Additionally, the system uses existing proof corpora to generate recommendations, which involves machine learning techniques, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The system also aims to transfer expertise from experienced users to new users, which falls under the category of cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the use of special purpose proof methods, which relates to cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
